00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:38.140
=Episode 7=
(Twin Cultivation on Full Moon Night)

00:00:47.960 --> 00:00:49.360
(Why is my face so red?)

00:00:58.720 --> 00:01:00.120
(What am I even thinking?)

00:01:00.560 --> 00:01:01.400
(Calm down.)

00:01:02.280 --> 00:01:03.680
(Calm down.)

00:01:04.440 --> 00:01:05.960
(It's the Silver Fox Clan scent.)

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:16.720
(I knew there was a hidden chamber.)

00:01:17.360 --> 00:01:19.200
(The account might be hidden here.)

00:01:43.565 --> 00:01:44.640
(Oh no.)

00:02:28.320 --> 00:02:29.360
Why are you here?

00:02:29.640 --> 00:02:30.920
I didn't summon you.

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:40.320
I'll be careful.

00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:41.040
You...

00:02:41.480 --> 00:02:42.720
What are you doing in the study?

00:02:47.160 --> 00:02:48.960
It was Lord Yi who framed my father

00:02:49.240 --> 00:02:50.800
and got my whole family executed.

00:02:51.610 --> 00:02:52.560
I came to Lord Yi's Residence

00:02:52.560 --> 00:02:54.040
for one reason only.

00:02:54.440 --> 00:02:55.640
I want to avenge the Mu family.

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:58.040
If that's so,

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:00.040
I'll help you kill him.

00:03:01.520 --> 00:03:02.920
I want blood for blood,

00:03:03.260 --> 00:03:04.640
but more than that,
I want to clear our name.

00:03:05.040 --> 00:03:05.840
I must find the evidence

00:03:05.840 --> 00:03:07.160
that he framed my father

00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:08.640
and prove the Mu family's innocence.

00:03:09.640 --> 00:03:11.360
I just tested Ji Yuanying

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:14.200
and found out there maybe
a secret account hidden here,

00:03:15.240 --> 00:03:16.760
but I didn't find it yet.

00:03:17.160 --> 00:03:18.080
I suspect

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:19.920
there's a hidden space here.

00:04:25.920 --> 00:04:26.720
I'll keep looking.

00:04:50.920 --> 00:04:52.080
I knew there was a secret chamber.

00:04:52.760 --> 00:04:53.080
Come on.

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:54.480
Help me look for it.

00:05:00.080 --> 00:05:01.600
Lord Yi took so many bribes.

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:03.240
Once we find the secret account,

00:05:03.520 --> 00:05:05.160
he can never deny it before His Majesty.

00:05:09.200 --> 00:05:09.920
It's here.

00:05:17.080 --> 00:05:18.280
Indeed.

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:24.600
Quick. Get out of here first.

00:05:45.080 --> 00:05:46.600
(No way, the lock.)

00:06:25.480 --> 00:06:27.720
(What to do? He's going to see us.)

00:07:30.480 --> 00:07:31.480
What's wrong?

00:07:34.520 --> 00:07:35.160
Nothing.

00:07:35.920 --> 00:07:36.840
Let's get out of here.

00:07:52.080 --> 00:07:53.600
He almost found us.

00:07:54.720 --> 00:07:55.280
Thank you.

00:07:57.160 --> 00:07:58.200
That day

00:07:58.200 --> 00:08:00.840
when you pulled out a golden feather,
I was conscious.

00:08:01.480 --> 00:08:03.520
The golden feather must be important

00:08:03.760 --> 00:08:04.960
to Phoenix Divine Beasts, right?

00:08:10.280 --> 00:08:14.480
If he ever takes over your body again,

00:08:15.080 --> 00:08:15.960
I can help you.

00:08:16.480 --> 00:08:17.160
You know?

00:08:18.600 --> 00:08:20.800
I know there are two souls in your body,

00:08:21.280 --> 00:08:22.280
and my kiss

00:08:22.720 --> 00:08:24.080
can keep it at bay.

00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:30.040
There won't be another time like this.

00:08:30.400 --> 00:08:31.280
I help you

00:08:32.640 --> 00:08:34.080
only for the Xuanzhu Jade.

00:09:33.960 --> 00:09:35.240
What's wrong with me?

00:09:50.800 --> 00:09:52.450
(After the twin cultivation
on the full moon night,)

00:09:52.880 --> 00:09:54.960
(she will be sacrificed
once the pact is complete.)

00:09:55.840 --> 00:09:57.800
(For the sake of the clan,
I mustn't have feelings for her.)

00:10:07.720 --> 00:10:09.240
Ah, I've lost my mind.

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:18.080
Could it be...

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:20.480
"Twin cultivation
on the full moon night.

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:22.600
Whoever betrays

00:10:22.840 --> 00:10:24.200
will suffer backlashes."

00:10:24.960 --> 00:10:25.840
Does that mean

00:10:26.440 --> 00:10:28.240
he and I...

00:11:00.200 --> 00:11:00.720
You...

00:11:01.600 --> 00:11:02.720
- I...
- I...

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:07.120
You...

00:11:07.480 --> 00:11:09.200
It's late. Why are you in my room?

00:11:10.640 --> 00:11:11.320
I couldn't sleep,

00:11:12.200 --> 00:11:13.080
so I passed by.

00:11:16.880 --> 00:11:17.200
You...

00:11:17.320 --> 00:11:18.600
You're dressed so boldly,

00:11:19.320 --> 00:11:20.480
wandering around at midnight.

00:11:22.640 --> 00:11:23.800
The Scarlet Flame Clan

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:25.280
has warm bodies.

00:11:27.080 --> 00:11:27.840
I should get going.

00:11:27.840 --> 00:11:29.200
Wait. Don't go.

00:11:36.440 --> 00:11:38.360
No. Just go.

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:41.880
Do you want me to come in

00:11:42.840 --> 00:11:44.120
or to go out?

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:18.080
Backlash is nothing.

00:12:18.720 --> 00:12:20.200
I won't believe I can't get through it.

00:12:23.080 --> 00:12:23.720
Sleep.

00:12:24.080 --> 00:12:25.240
Just sleep and it'll be fine.

00:12:38.605 --> 00:12:39.440
(Calm down.)

00:12:40.560 --> 00:12:41.440
(Calm down.)

00:12:52.360 --> 00:12:53.240
(Calm down.)

00:12:53.840 --> 00:12:54.720
(Calm down.)

00:13:21.480 --> 00:13:21.880
I...

00:13:22.200 --> 00:13:23.000
I didn't

00:13:23.360 --> 00:13:24.360
mean it.

00:13:24.880 --> 00:13:26.360
I didn't mean to summon you.

00:13:32.960 --> 00:13:34.000
I don't care.

00:13:34.960 --> 00:13:37.280
You started it.

00:14:04.680 --> 00:14:07.240
=Twin Fates=
=End of Episode 7=

